text: I would be pleased if peeps just report the haters and I will certainly return and try to communicate some of my views and specific ideas. But I don't have time or inclination to deal with the shark attacks anymore.

sorry but i didnt tweet this morning as i have been taking a sabbatical from twitter because of the vitriol and hate from sharks like you that make it impossible to reach the good fish. your lies and hate ruin twitter for everyone.
